				<title>MyBatis（四）：缓存机制与源码解析</title>
				<link>https://liwenqikeep.github.io/posts/mybatis%E5%9B%9B%E7%BC%93%E5%AD%98%E6%9C%BA%E5%88%B6%E4%B8%8E%E6%BA%90%E7%A0%81%E8%A7%A3%E6%9E%90/</link>
